ACROSS THE N OF THE UK. THROUGH MONDAY THIS LOW MOVS SLWY S AND E BRINGING
A FRONTAL TROUGH SE ACROSS THE UK AND MAINTAINING A STRG NW FLOW ACROSS ALL
